            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_47gc' title='Col. 47GC &mdash; HL Deb 23 January 2001 vol 621 c47GC' name='column_47gc' href='#column_47gc' rel='bookmark'>47GC</a>
            It makes it a more general problem of how the child's voice should be heard rather than one specifically relating to Clause 1(3).
          </p>
